    <UADataType NodeId="ns=1;i=3002" BrowseName="1:OperatingModeEnumeration">
        <DisplayName>OperatingModeEnumeration</DisplayName>
        <Description>Actual operating mode of the TCD</Description>
        <References>
            <Reference ReferenceType="HasProperty">ns=1;i=7147</Reference>
            <Reference ReferenceType="HasSubtype" IsForward="false">i=29</Reference>
        </References>
        <Definition Name="1:OperatingModeEnumeration">
            <Field Name="OTHER" Value="0">
                <Description>Operating mode of the TCD is unknown</Description>
            </Field>
            <Field Name="READY_TO_OPERATE" Value="1">
                <Description>TCD is ready to operate (heating, pump and cooling are switched off)</Description>
            </Field>
            <Field Name="NORMAL_OPERATION" Value="2">
                <Description>TCD is running in normal operating mode</Description>
            </Field>
            <Field Name="LEAK_STOPPER" Value="3">
                <Description>TCD is running in leak stopper operating mode</Description>
            </Field>
            <Field Name="MOULD_EVACUATION" Value="4">
                <Description>TCD is carrying out a mould evacuation process</Description>
            </Field>
            <Field Name="PRESSURE_RELIEF" Value="5">
                <Description>TCD is carrying out a pressure relief process</Description>
            </Field>
            <Field Name="COOLING" Value="6">
                <Description>TCD is cooling down to StandbyTemperature and switch off</Description>
            </Field>
            <Field Name="SAFETY_COOLING" Value="7">
                <Description>TCD is cooling down to SwitchingOffTemperature and switch off</Description>
            </Field>
            <Field Name="ECO" Value="8">
                <Description>TCD is running in Eco operating mode (energy is saved via the reduced pump speed)</Description>
            </Field>
            <Field Name="BOOST" Value="9">
                <Description>TCD is running in Boost operating mode (pump runs at maximum possible speed)</Description>
            </Field>
        </Definition>
    </UADataType>
